b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":891,"category_name":"Maintenance","pr_category_id":"3","title_name":"Maintenance Notice for 11\/27(PT)[Update]","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574924400\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>Maintenance was completed at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574924400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send a gift of 300 wyrmite to all players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574917199\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><hr><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574920620\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>Please be aware that the maintenance has been extended.<br>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.<br><br>Maintenance is scheduled to end on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574924400\\"><\/span>.<br>Thank you for your patience.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>We will be performing maintenance during the following period to prepare for a future update and change how the dojo facilities are obtained. You will not be able to obtain rewards if you complete a quest during the maintenance period. Please also claim any 30-Day Pack (Recovery) rewards before maintenance begins.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Maintenance Period<\/div><div>Around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574917200\\"><\/span> to around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574920800\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Regarding Changes to How Dojos are Obtained<\/div><div>The way that dojos are obtained will change after this maintenance is complete.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcBefore<\/div><div>Use items to trade for the dojo facilities in the Treasure Trade for The Imperial Onslaught.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcAfter<\/div><div>When Chapter 6 \/ 4-4 of the main campaign, Diadem of Light, is cleared, two of each type of dojo will be added to the Adventurers tab of the Storehouse under Castle Grounds.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcApplicable Facilities<\/div><div>\\u30fbSword Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of sword-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbBlade Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of blade-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbDagger Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of dagger-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbAxe Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of axe-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbLance Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of lance-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbBow Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of bow-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbWand Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of wand-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbStaff Dojo<\/div><div>Boosts the stats of staff-wielding adventurers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Compensation Accompanying These Changes<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>1. If you have completed Chapter 6 \/ 4-4 of the main campaign, Diadem of Light, but have not traded for the dojos:<\/div><div>Any dojos you have not traded for will be delivered to your goodie box.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>2. If you have completed Chapter 6 \/ 4-4 of the main campaign, Diadem of Light, and have already traded for the dojos:<\/div><div>The items used to trade for the dojos will be returned to you.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbWe will be handling this compensation after the maintenance is completed, but please understand that it may take some time to complete.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The game will be inaccessible during maintenance.<\/div><div>2. Maintenance may start and\/or end before or after the scheduled times.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div>","start_time":1574316000,"prev_article_id":"866","next_article_id":"943","image_path":"","update_time":1574924523}}}'